{"word":"Lamp","slug":"lamp","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Lamp</b> Miraculously appeared at Abraham's sacrifice<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=15&verse=17'>Gen 15:17</a><br/> For the tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=25&verse=40'>Exo 25:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=37&verse=22'>Exo 37:22</a><br/> Kept burning at night in the tabernacle and cared for by priests<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=27&verse=21'>Exo 27:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=24&verse=4'>Lev 24:4</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=18&verse=6'>Job 18:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=119&verse=105'>Psa 119:105</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=13&verse=9'>Pro 13:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=20&verse=20'>Pro 20:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=62&verse=1'>Isa 62:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=25&verse=10'>Jer 25:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=36&chapter=1&verse=12'>Zep 1:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=6&verse=22'>Mat 6:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=1&verse=19'>2Pe 1:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=21&verse=23'>Rev 21:23</a><br/> Symbolic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=4&verse=5'>Rev 4:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=8&verse=10'>Rev 8:10</a><br/><a href='S:Candlestick'>Candlestick</a>"}]}